\newlabel{fig:appendix_revenue_margin}{{17}{11}{\textbf {Margin Compression:} While top-line revenue has grown consistently, gross margin percentage has compressed, demonstrating that the current acquisition engine relies on unsustainable promotional pricing}{figure.caption.20}{}}
